ledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180722%2F58472155&d=3ITnXFeXHbdOyeto2v6EzZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=99f65749\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180722%2F58472155&h=a7e6c58f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180722/58472155</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130626/18312899\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130626%2F18312899&d=3ITnXFeXHbdOyeto2v6EzZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4e0cd4df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130626%2F18312899&h=f02591f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130626/18312899</a><br />\n<br />\n【內地禁洋垃圾】無法輸出廢膠去中國 日企破產摺埋上海加工廠<br />\n<br />\n《日本經濟新聞》報道，中國今年禁止進口塑膠廢棄物，已開始影響依賴中國的日本貿易商，部份業者面臨破產，其他業者則調整策略。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，日本福岡縣一家塑膠廢棄物公司3月聲請破產，總部設在茨城縣的亞星商事今年底前則會關閉該公司位於上海的加工廠。亞星商事原本把廢棄塑膠出口至這座工廠，但隨着中國禁止進口塑膠廢棄物，這座工廠已無用武之地。業內人士則估計，日本其他廢膠出口商也可能破產或停止營運。<br />\n2016年中國進口約730萬公噸廢棄塑膠，相當於全球出口一半以上，其中約130萬公噸來自日本，這些塑膠被改造成日常用品。不過，中國政府為對付環境污染，今年開始實施廢棄塑膠和廢紙的進口禁令。<br />\n<br />\n去到中國咪又係丟返落海"},{"pid":"e5f817698768676698ffc1438226f9358c8d972d","tid":775713,"uid":887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f742cddff9ce381674394409e1b3a53815d3d7","tid":775713,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:23:16.000Z","msg":"海龜真係累事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}